room_title: Escape room "The Zodiac" by Get a Clue Games in Baltimore
room_address: 8019 Corporate Dr Suite J Nottingham, MD 21236
room_description:
You finally got a lucky break as a journalist when you received a tip about the whereabouts of an active serial killer with a passion for photography. You’re eager to confirm this lead, warn the authorities and write an amazing follow-up story. But you know this type of work proves beyond dangerous, so you chose not to go alone.
Turns out your gut feeling was right. The killer has been taunting the police and the press for years with unsolved riddles that lead nowhere and now you’re stuck right in the middle of it. After running through the forest for hours, you finally stumble upon what appears to be a cozy cabin. However, once inside, you realize you made a mistake. You hope your instincts can save you in time.
